title: An Alternative to Pumpkin for Your Pie
text:
An Alternative to Pumpkin for Your Pie 
With all of the worry over Pumpkin Puree, NewsChannel9 went to find a solution. There should be enough Pumpkin cans for your pie, but there is an alternative, Butternut Squash. "Pumpkin is a Winter Squash, which doesn't necessarily mean it grows in the winter, it prefers warm weather, but it stores in the cold," said Paul Peterson, a farmer at Crabtree Farms An Alternative to Pumpkin for Your Pie Saturday, October 10 2015, 01:47 PM
